{"tid":694079,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【一問三答】12000元月供6隻股票","createTime":"2018-06-08T04:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T06:07:39.000Z","uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"547caccd9f49de7a90613140e07e6f8e38f6a776","tid":694079,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"讀者區先生問：「以12000元月供6隻股票，包括騰訊(00700)，恒生銀行(00011)，銀河娛樂(00027)，華人置業(00127)，中華煤氣(00003)及盈富基金(02800)。我現在35歲，想月供10年，是否可行？整個組合可以嗎，要轉換那隻股份？我已經供了一年，如果加多隻港鐵(00066)，可以嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n沈振盈   訊匯證券行政總裁 <br />\n<br />\n首先要了解月供股票的意義，就是避免承受太大的風險，尤其大市波動時，能夠有平均的入市法。惟近年市況波動大，大升之餘，當周期向下時，會大跌至底部。若以近周期頂部進行月供，會拉高入市平均價，我建議作出一些調節。當大市到周期頂部時，減低月供的比例，甚至停供待調整過後低吸。另一方面，我覺得你的組合需要作出一些調配，我不太建議加入港鐵。至於，騰訊已經超出價值，應該先行獲利剔除或減少月供比例，銀娛更是值得獲利停供，恒生可以視乎情況，但因估值太昂貴，都是建議停供。而我會建議整個組合可加入石油股，特別是中海油(00883)及中石油(00857)，另外亦可考慮黃金ETF及聯想集團(00992)。」"},{"pid":"fb9a2681aee4eadd0b5ef8c00c1f1d50821d7fcb","tid":694079,"uid":5081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"佢建議個4隻.................<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab63f7bb10419bd98cdd59e777008d7c64eed2b","tid":694079,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9a2681aee4eadd0b5ef8c00c1f1d50821d7fcb","tid":694079,"uid":5081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"佢建議個4隻.................<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f83259b478758c2fab1f08cccfd2e470dd429f0","tid":694079,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"而我會建議整個組合可加入保險及電訊股，特別是中人壽(02628)及中移動(00941)，另外亦可考慮聯想集團(00992)。」"},{"pid":"f1ece01752966aac28e6b198176cfff095d1fb3d","tid":694079,"uid":174124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5d09aaf42bd78bcf9391c5cf60b810ab4701d9","tid":694079,"uid":27004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93eb0ed749794d335c45be87a2b064416896d4d1","tid":694079,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f83259b478758c2fab1f08cccfd2e470dd429f0","tid":694079,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"而我會建議整個組合可加入保險及電訊股，特別是中人壽(02628)及中移動(00941)，另外亦可考慮聯想集團(00992)。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"求其入4隻都好過佢啦"},{"pid":"fee5c01f219ef7d30bd34084a192dfa80f6a8c17","tid":694079,"uid":123790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"銀娛更是值得獲利停供<br />\n呢個佢講中晒"},{"pid":"25335e61a1ee9a89ab7919d21b7206fca722f6df","tid":694079,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fee5c01f219ef7d30bd34084a192dfa80f6a8c17","tid":694079,"uid":123790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"銀娛更是值得獲利停供<br />\n呢個佢講中晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"20